name: DEM
description: CrazyFarm is a chain game platform based on a decentralized income farm. Its contracts are deployed on Binance Smart Chain and aim to combine games and digital collectibles to build a high-performance composite Metaverse ecosystem. In CrazyFarm, players can combine entertainment and profitability through pet battles and farm farming, raising pets, or growing farmland. Each NFT pet in Crazy Farm has a unique identity and is highly collectible. EDM is Crazy Farm's governance token. Holders of DEM and DEC earn DEM rewards by staking tokens.
